      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard and preserved in pristine showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a machine that exhibits no discernible wear, both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects a commitment to meticulous care, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 48900.0,
